Method_of_Evaluation:
Student presentation (individually or in groups, depending on student enrolment for the course) = 30%;
Seminar participation = 30%;
End of semester written short response paper = 40%.

The method of evaluation is by continuous assessment (hence, there is no final exam). A final grade will be given based on:

1. student presentation (individually or in groups, depending on student enrolment) = 30%;
2. seminar participation = 30%;
3. end of semester written assignment of a short response paper = 40%.

